Also includes cadatral maps of specific land parcels, with lots, and lot numbers. Available also through the Library of Congress Web site as a raster image. Romanized; maps in Thai scripts. Predominant scale 1:4,000.

description: Some maps dated as Rō̜. Sō̜. 125 for Phō̜. Sō̜. 2449 or 1906. Relief shown by hachures on some maps. Maps of Lop Burī Province published by Thai Royal Survey Department in the central region of Thailand. Lop Burī is on the east side of the Chao Phraya River valley.
